#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.to_lance.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.to\\_lance"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_lance.to_lance:1 of
msgid "Write a DataFrame to a Lance dataset."
msgstr "将 DataFrame 写入 Lance 数据集。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_lance.to_lance:3 of
msgid ""
"Lance is a columnar data format optimized for ML workloads and vector "
"search. Each chunk will be written as a fragment."
msgstr ""
"Lance 是一种为 ML 工作负载和向量搜索优化的列式数据格式。每个数据块将被"
"写入为一个片段。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_lance.to_lance of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_lance.to_lance:6 of
msgid ""
"Target path for the Lance dataset. Can be a local path, Aliyun OSS URL, "
"or S3 URL. For Aliyun OSS URLs, the format is: "
"``oss://<endpoint>/<bucket>/<path>``. Example: ``oss://oss-cn-"
"beijing.aliyuncs.com/my-bucket/dataset``. For S3 URLs, the format is: "
"``s3://<bucket>/<path>``."
msgstr ""
"Lance 数据集的目标路径。可以是本地路径、阿里云 OSS URL 或 S3 URL。对于"
"阿里云 OSS URL，格式为：``oss://<endpoint>/<bucket>/<path>``。示例：``oss"
"://oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/my-bucket/dataset``。对于 S3 URL，格式为："
"``s3://<bucket>/<path>``。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_lance.to_lance:12 of
msgid ""
"How to handle existing data: - 'create': Create a new dataset (fails if "
"exists) - 'append': Append to existing dataset - 'overwrite': Overwrite "
"existing dataset"
msgstr ""
"如何处理现有数据：- 'create'：创建新数据集（如果已存在则失败）- 'append'"
"：追加到现有数据集 - 'overwrite'：覆盖现有数据集"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_lance.to_lance:17 of
msgid ""
"If True, write DataFrame index as a column. If False, do not write the "
"index. If None (default), write the index only if it's not a simple "
"RangeIndex (same as ``pa.Table.from_pandas`` default behavior)."
msgstr ""
"如果为 True，则将 DataFrame 索引作为列写入。如果为 False，则不写入索引。"
"如果为 None（默认），则仅在索引不是简单的 RangeIndex 时写入索引（与 ``pa."
"Table.from_pandas`` 的默认行为相同）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_lance.to_lance:21 of
msgid ""
"Column label(s) for the index column(s). If None (default) and `index` is"
" True, the index names are used. Use this to rename the index column when"
" writing (e.g., from '_idx_0' to 'id')."
msgstr ""
"索引列的列标签。如果为 None（默认）且 `index` 为 True，则使用索引名称。"
"使用此参数可在写入时重命名索引列（例如，从 '_idx_0' 重命名为 'id'）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_lance.to_lance:25 of
msgid ""
"PyArrow schema to specify column types, compression, encoding, etc. "
"Columns in this schema will override auto-detected types from DataFrame. "
"Columns not specified will use types inferred from DataFrame."
msgstr ""
"用于指定列类型、压缩、编码等的 PyArrow 模式。此模式中的列将覆盖从 "
"DataFrame 自动检测的类型。未指定的列将使用从 DataFrame 推断的类型。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_lance.to_lance:29 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Options for storage connection. For Aliyun OSS with RAM role: "
"``{'role_arn': 'acs:ram::xxx:role/name'}`` For Aliyun OSS with AK/SK: "
"``{'access_key_id': 'xxx', 'access_key_secret': 'xxx'}`` For S3: "
"``{'aws_access_key_id': 'xxx', 'aws_secret_access_key': 'xxx'}``"
msgstr ""
"存储连接选项。对于使用 RAM 角色的阿里云 OSS：``{'role_arn': 'acs:ram::xxx"
":role/name'}`` 对于使用 AK/SK 的阿里云 OSS：``{'access_key_id': 'xxx', '"
"access_key_secret': 'xxx'}`` 对于 S3：``{'aws_access_key_id': 'xxx', 'aws"
"_secret_access_key': 'xxx'}``"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_lance.to_lance:34 of
msgid "Additional keyword arguments passed to lance.fragment.write_fragments()."
msgstr "传递给 lance.fragment.write_fragments() 的额外关键字参数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_lance.to_lance of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_lance.to_lance:36 of
msgid "An empty DataFrame (write operation result)."
msgstr "一个空的 DataFrame（写入操作的结果）。"

